---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Layout title="Playlister">
  <main>
    <Card
      title="Back"
      body=""
      href="/"
      classes="fixed"
      external={false}
      flipped={true}
    />
    <h1 class="center">
      <span class="text-gradient">Playlister</span>
    </h1>
    <div class="body sidemargins">
      <p class="center top-margin">
        <i>
          A project originally focusing on the basics of React state, which I
          expanded to include media playback. Includes sorting, filtering, and
          aggregation of songs into a playlist.
        </i>
      </p>
      <div class="center">
        <a href="/playlister" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
          <img
            width="75%"
            src="../media/playlister/cover.png"
            alt="A cover image for the application."
          />
        </a>
        <p>
          <a href="/playlister" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
            <i>Figure 1. Main view of the application.</i>
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="section" style="width: 70%">
        <h2>
          <span class="text-gradient">Objective</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          This application was created as part of a basic React assignment for
          my UI/UX class. We were to create a list of items, with filtering,
          sorting, and aggregating functionality. I chose songs as my type of
          item. Since I had been using React for quite some time at that point,
          I elected to augment the application to include media playback of the
          songs as well.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      style="display:flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"
    >
      <div class="section">
        <div class="center" style="justify-content: center;">
          <p>
            Thanks for visiting my project! <br />
            <span class="text-gradient">â™¡</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
<style>
  :root {
    --astro-gradient: linear-gradient(0deg, #b9b0ff, #d179c0);
  }

  main {
    color: white;
  }

  a {
    color: #62c4da;
  }

  a:visited {
    color: #da62c4;
  }

  ul {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
  }

  pre {
    display: inline;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .center {
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .sidemargins {
    margin: 0 7rem;
  }

  .image {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    background-color: white;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .top-margin {
    margin-top: 0.875rem;
  }

  .bottom-margin {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section {
    background-color: rgb(50, 50, 50);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    align-self: center;
  }

  .text-gradient {
    font-weight: 900;
    background-image: var(--astro-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-size: 100% 200%;
    background-position-y: 100%;
    border-radius: 0.4rem;
    animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%,
    100% {
      background-position-y: 0%;
    }
    50% {
      background-position-y: 80%;
    }
  }
</style>
